high_descs: Turn left, go past refrigerator, turn right.  Go to wall, turn left, proceed to stove.
Pick up pot from back right burner of stove.
Turn left, proceed to counter between microwave and sink.
Put pot in left side of sink, turn water on and off, drain water.  Pick up pot from sink.
Turn around, go to wall.  Turn left and proceed to refrigerator.
Open refrigerator, place pot on top right shelf, close refrigerator door.
anns.task_desc: Pick up pot from stove, wash pot, put pot in refrigerator.

high_descs: Turn left and veer slightly right to the stove.
Pick up the pot on the right burner.
Turn left and walk to the sink.
Wash the pot in the sink.
Turn around and veer left to the fridge.
Place the pot in the fridge on the right top shelf.
anns.task_desc: Place a rinsed pot in a fridge.

high_descs: turn left and walk over to the kitchen stove on the right
grab a pot off of the right side of the kitchen stove
turn left and walk over to the left side of the kitchen sink on the right at the end of the room
clean the pot off inside the kitchen sink
turn right and walk over to the refrigerator at the right side corner of the room
place the pot inside of the refrigerator
anns.task_desc: place a clean pot inside of the refrigerator
